  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Area of baseline transcranial motor evoked potentials (TcMEPs) prior to desflurane and after desflurane.</measure>
    <time_frame>15 minutes</time_frame>
    <description>The area of baseline TcMEPs will be calculated for three different muscle groups. TcMEP area is again calculated after desflurane. This data is collected at the beginning and end of surgery.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
